    "## your code here\n",
    "\n",
    "#Easier version\n",
    "#df_airpl.groupby(\"Aircraft Series\")[\"Aircraft Series\"].agg(['count']).sort_values(\"count\", ascending = False).head(10)\n",
    "\n",
    "#Harder version\n",
    "df_airpl[\"count\"] = df_airpl.groupby('Aircraft Series')['Aircraft Series'].transform('count')\n",
    "df_airpl_engage = df_airpl.groupby(\"Aircraft Series\")[\"count\"].first().reset_index().sort_values(\"count\", ascending = False).head(10)\n",
    "df_airpl_engage[\"Percentage\"] = df_airpl_engage[\"count\"] / df_airpl_engage[\"count\"].sum()\n",
    "\n",
    "df_airpl_engage\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.pie(df_airpl_engage[\"Percentage\"], labels = df_airpl_engage[\"Aircraft Series\"], autopct = '%1.1f%%')\n",
    "plt.legend(df_airpl_engage[\"Aircraft Series\"], loc = \"best\")\n",
    "\n"
